      "description": "## Codex Usage 0.1.2\n\nFirst community-review build of Codex Usage for Obsidian.\n\n### Included\n\n- Managed, checksum-verified CodexBar helpers for macOS arm64/x64 and Windows x64\n- Session and weekly usage, credits, cost data, reset windows, and raw output\n- Persistent last-good cache and delayed startup refresh\n- Dashboard, status bar, settings, diagnostics, and local logs\n- Verified GitHub artifact attestations for all Obsidian release assets\n\nHelpers are installed only after explicit confirmation and are not silently updated. This is an independent project and is not affiliated with OpenAI, Obsidian, CodexBar, or Win-CodexBar.",
